divs: Sighting DetailsI was letting my dog, wuf, out for some fresh air when I noticed a bright light over the city skyline. I immediately grabbed my phone to take a picture and I'm glad I did that because two seconds later the light suddenly took off at incredible speed. It can't have been a falling star or an airplane, because they don't move that fast. Did anybody else see it?
